<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="習禪" xml:id="gsz0761a11shiHuaiRang"><lb
ed="T" n="0761a11"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0761a11"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000028941">南嶽觀音臺</placeName><persName key="A004015">懷讓</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0761a12"/><persName key="A004015">釋懷讓</persName>，俗姓<name>杜</name>，<placeName key="PL000000044413">金州安康</placeName>人也<ptr target="#n369"/>。始<date key="j19716171971981" from-iso="+0686-01-01" to-iso="+0686-12-31">年十歲</date>，雅<lb
ed="T" n="0761a13"/>好佛書，炳然殊姿，特有靈表，識者占是出家<lb
ed="T" n="0761a14"/>相，非染俗貴。人寶<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1439"/>來瑞，國慶無疆，方之麟<lb
ed="T" n="0761a15"/>鳳龜龍，無萬數也。天地無全功<ptr target="#n1384"/>，氣序有盈<lb
ed="T" n="0761a16"/>虛<ptr target="#n1385"/>，綱維缺壞，補塞不足，皆冥維密祐，惟應<lb
ed="T" n="0761a17"/>度<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1440"/>者乃燭厥理，非庸庸所知也。<ref target="#j19752691975634" type="date">弱冠</ref><ptr target="#n370"/>詣<placeName key="PL000000027023">荊<lb
ed="T" n="0761a18"/>南玉泉寺</placeName>，事<persName key="A008970">恒景<roleName>律師</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n1388"/>，便剃髮受具<ptr target="#n1386"/>。歎曰：「夫<lb
ed="T" n="0761a19"/>出家者為無為法<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1441"/>，天上人間無有勝者，經<lb
ed="T" n="0761a20"/>之所謂出四衢道露地而坐也。<ptr target="#n1387"/>」時<persName key="A010231">坦<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n374"/>乃<lb
ed="T" n="0761a21"/>勸<persName key="A004015">讓</persName>往<placeName key="PL000000023253">嵩丘</placeName>覿<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1442"/><persName key="A010232">安<roleName>公</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n1389"/>，<persName key="A010232">安</persName>啟發之，因入<placeName key="PL000000030577">曹侯<lb
ed="T" n="0761a22"/>溪</placeName>，覲<persName key="A001719">能<roleName>公</roleName></persName>。<persName key="A001719">能<roleName>公</roleName></persName>怡然，無馨無臭，洪波泛臻<lb
ed="T" n="0761a23"/>大壑之廣乎？《<anchor xml:id="beg0761002"/>韶濩<anchor xml:id="end0761002"/>》<ptr target="#n1390"/>合奏大樂之和乎？<persName key="A004015">讓</persName>之深<lb
ed="T" n="0761a24"/>入寂定，住<placeName key="PL000000030580">無動道場</placeName>，為若此也。<persName key="A001719">能<roleName>公</roleName></persName>大事<lb
ed="T" n="0761a25"/>緣畢，<persName key="A004015">讓</persName>乃躋<placeName key="PL000000028928">衡嶽</placeName>，止于<placeName key="PL000000028941">觀音臺</placeName><ptr target="#n1392"/>。時有<persName key="A010233">僧玄</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0761a26"/>至拘刑獄，舉念願<persName key="A004015">讓<roleName>師</roleName></persName>救護。<persName key="A004015">讓</persName>早知而勉<lb
ed="T" n="0761a27"/><ref type="person" target="#A010233">之</ref>，其僧脫難，云是「救苦觀音」，得斯號也亦<lb
ed="T" n="0761a28"/>由此焉。化緣斯盡，傳法弟子曰<persName key="A010236">道峻</persName>，曰<persName key="A003623">道<lb
ed="T" n="0761a29"/>一</persName>，皆升堂覩奧也。其後<persName key="A003623">一<roleName>公</roleName></persName>振法鼓于<placeName key="PL000000018628">洪<pb ed="T" n="0761b" xml:id="T50.2061.0761b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0761b01"/>州</placeName>，其門弟子曰<persName key="A010237">惟寬</persName>、<persName key="A010238">懷暉</persName>。<persName key="A003623">道一</persName>大緣將訖，謂<lb
ed="T" n="0761b02"/><persName key="A010237">寬</persName>等曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A004015">吾師</ref>之道存乎妙者也，無待而常，<lb
ed="T" n="0761b03"/>不住而至，能事集矣。金口所生，從法而化，<lb
ed="T" n="0761b04"/>於<ref type="person" target="#A003623">我</ref>為子，及<ref type="person" target="#A010237 #A010238">汝</ref>為孫，一燈所傳，何有盡者？」<lb
ed="T" n="0761b05"/><persName key="A004015">讓</persName>以<date from-iso="+0677-02-11" key="j19683711968724" to-iso="+0678-01-30">儀鳳二年</date>生，至<date key="j19930671993067" when-iso="+0744-09-24"><name>天寶</name>三載八月十日</date><ptr target="#n1391"/><lb
ed="T" n="0761b06"/>終于<placeName key="PL000000028928">衡嶽</placeName>，春秋六十八，僧臘四十八。<persName key="A003623">一<roleName>公</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0761b07"/>建塔于別峯。<date notBefore-iso="+0806-01-29" key="j20154742020606" notAfter-iso="+0820-02-17"><name>元和</name>中</date><ptr target="#n375"/>，<persName key="A010237">寬</persName>、<persName key="A010238">暉</persName>至<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京師</ref>，揚其本<lb
ed="T" n="0761b08"/>宗，法門大啟，傳百千燈。<placeName key="PL000000000083">京夏</placeName>法寶鴻緒，於<lb
ed="T" n="0761b09"/>斯為盛。至<date from-iso="+0813-02-09" key="j20180422018395" to-iso="+0814-01-28">八載</date>，<placeName key="PL000000028912">衡陽</placeName>太守<persName key="A010234">令狐權</persName>問<persName key="A004015">讓</persName>前<lb
ed="T" n="0761b10"/>迹，<persName key="A010234">權</persName>捨衣財以充忌齋。自此每歲八月為<lb
ed="T" n="0761b11"/>「觀音忌」焉。<date notBefore-iso="+0825-02-02" key="j20224182023191" notAfter-iso="+0827-03-17">寶曆中</date>，勅諡<persName key="A004015">大慧禪師</persName>，塔號<placeName key="PL000000056373">最<lb
ed="T" n="0761b12"/>勝輪</placeName>。<date notBefore-iso="+0806-01-29" key="j20154742020606" notAfter-iso="+0820-02-17"><name>元和</name>年中</date>常侍<persName key="A009183">歸登</persName>撰碑云。</p>
